        <h1 class="w-full mb-4 font-serif text-4xl font-bold uppercase sm:w-auto sm:text-5xl text-oak sm:mb-0">
          The Rook
        </h1>
        <hr class="w-4/5 mx-auto border-2 sm:w-auto sm:flex-1 border-oak sm:mx-0">
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg">
        <p>
          The rook moves in straight lines, either horizontally or vertically, across the board. It can cover a lot of
          ground quickly and is particularly powerful in open positions. It can also work well with other pieces,
          coordinating attacks and controlling key squares.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rooks are strongest in open files and ranks, where they can control long stretches of the board. Mastering the
          rook helps you dominate the game and create powerful threats!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

